    "upstream eval ok: basic/parens (gold match)"
    "upstream eval ok: basic/import1 (gold match)"
    "upstream eval ok: basic/baseModule (gold match)"
    "upstream eval ok: basic/comments (gold match)"
    "upstream eval ok: basic/indexExpressions (gold match)"
    "upstream eval ok: classes/class1 (gold match)"
